        "block_label": "figure_title",
        "block_content": "Figure 1: The overview of REDIFFUSE. We independently input the image to the variation API n times with diffusion step t. We take the average of the output images and compare them with the original ones. If the difference is below a certain threshold, we determine that the image is in the training set.",
