        "block_label": "figure_title",
        "block_content": "Figure 2: The intuition of our algorithm design. We denote $x$ as the target image, $\\hat{x}_i$ as the $i$-th image generated by the variation API, and $\\hat{x}$ as the average image of them. For member image $x$, the difference $v = x - \\hat{x}$ will be smaller after averaging due to $x_i$ being an unbiased estimator.",
